NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN THAT, pursuant to the provisions of
the Nevada Revised Status, Robertson's Ready Mix, LTD
(hereinafter referred to as "Claimant") claims a lien upon the
real property and buildings, improvements or structures
thereon, described in Paragraph 6 below, and state the
following:
1.) That demand of Claimant, with the total of all labor
and/or materials supplied being $
1,083.42, and after
deducting all just credits, offsets, and payments
totaling $
0.00 is $
1,083.42 together with
interest thereon at the rate of 18% per annum from
2.) That the name of the owners or reputed owners of said
property is/are
RICHARD B. WALKER AND BEVERLY M. WALKER
3.) That the Claimant did from 02/14/2022, perform labor
and/or supply materials as follows: CONCRETE AND/OR
AGGREGATE for the construction, alteration, or repair of
said buildings, improvements, or structures, the location
of which is set forth in Paragraph 6 below.
4.) Claimant furnished work and materials under contract
with, or at the request of
ND CONCRETE LLC
The terms, time given and conditions of the contract
were: 10TH OF FOLLOWING MONTH
6. ) That the property upon which the lien is sought to be
charged is situated in the county of NYE (NV)
State of Nevada, described as:
1481 LAGUNA ST, PAHRUMP, NV 89048
